      "rationale": "The solver was verified against the ASME V&V 20 backward-facing step benchmark and a rotating-disk scalar transport manufactured solution. Observed order of accuracy matched the theoretical second-order convergence rate. Code verification requirements at gradation 2 are satisfied."
