      "rationale": "Bench tests were conducted at 2, 3, 4, 5, and 6 L/min at 3000 and 3500 RPM in a saline-glycerol blood analog (viscosity 3.5 cP, density 1056 kg/m³). Fluid properties and boundary conditions applied in CFD match bench measurements within 2%. Test conditions are adequately documented."
