      "rationale": "Predicted NIH values at the five operating points were compared against bench photometric measurements. Mean absolute prediction error was 9.4% with a 95% confidence interval of ±4.1%. All predicted RH values fell below 1.0. Output comparison satisfies gradation 2 requirements at the chosen settings."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
