      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry, which is the same geometry used in the COU. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB range (2–6 L/min, 3000–3500 RPM). Blood analog properties match clinical blood viscosity within 8%. Validation activities are adequately relevant to the COU."
