      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles, outlet pressure boundary conditions, rotational speed, fluid density, and viscosity are all documented with measurement sources and uncertainty ranges. Geometric dimensions were taken from the FDA benchmark CAD file (revision 3). Input uncertainty propagation was performed using a one-at-a-time sensitivity study. Model inputs are adequately characterized at gradation 2."
